# Build and Release Folders
# 👶 BabyTube - Safe Video Streaming Platform for Kids

BabyTube is a full-stack MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js) application designed to provide a safe and educational video streaming experience for children. The platform uses the YouTube Data API to display child-friendly videos while allowing parents to manage profiles, favorites, watch history, and screen time.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 👨‍👩‍👧 Parent Features
- Secure Registration & Login
- JWT Authentication
- Parent Dashboard
- Create & Manage Child Profiles
- Screen Time Control
- Watch History Monitoring
- Favorite Videos Management
